column2: SELECT id AS up_id,  ra AS up_ra,  dec AS up_dec FROM MYDB.datazhao  CREATE TABLE #tmp (   up_id varchar(#),   objid bigint ) INSERT INTO #tmp EXEC spGetNeighborsPrim #  INSERT INTO MYDB.out_zhao_# SELECT a.id, a.ra, a.dec, t.objid as matched_id, s.specObjID, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberID, s.ra, s.dec, s.z, e.EW_Ha_#, e.EW_Ha_#_Err FROM #tmp t   JOIN MYDB.datazhao a ON t.up_id = a.id   JOIN specobj s ON s.bestobjid=t.objid   JOIN galSpecInfo g on g.specObjID = s.specObjID   JOIN emissionLinesPort e on e.specObjID = s.specObjID
